 their ambassador in Warsaw, have been financing and organizing anti-Gomulka Stalinist elements in Poland.\n\nGomulka had not realized until recently that the Stalinists were backed by the Kremlin and \"were really out to cut his throat.\" Now that the elections are over, Gomulka \"will go after them\" and will try to get rid of those holding government and party offices and replace them with his own people. Gomulka's attitude toward his \"comrades\" was changing and that he \"is beginning to see who are his friends and who are his enemies in the party.\"\n\nComment\n\nGomulka will probably act to remove the Stalinists, but at the same time will probably try to prevent the press from voicing anti-Soviet sentiments and student and youth groups from making extreme demands", "token_count": 137, "token_end_0based": 136, "token_start_0based": 0, "token_text": "7 kremlin backs anti-gomulka elements in poland the russians through their ambassador in warsaw have been financing and organizing anti-gomulka stalinist elements in poland gomulka had not realized until recently that the stalinists were backed by the kremlin and were really out to cut his throat now that the elections are over gomulka will go after them and will try to get rid of those holding government and party offices and replace them with his own people gomulka's attitude toward his comrades was changing and that he is beginning to see who are his friends and who are his enemies in the party comment gomulka will probably act to remove the stalinists but at the same time will probably try to prevent the press from voicing anti-soviet sentiments and student and youth groups from making extreme demands", "unred_source_page": 9}
